			"height":40
		},
		{"id":"node_title","type":"text","text":"## ChatGPT模型的三层理解\n\n[[Sources/CuboxSync/ChatGPT模型的三层理解 - 张浩在路上-2023-09-07.md]]","x":-200,"y":-800,"width":520,"height":120},
		{"id":"node_11_pretrain","type":"text","text":"### 1.1 文字接龙（预训练）\n- 目标：预测下一个词/子词\n- 数据：海量未标注文本\n- 输出：概率分布，多样且不稳定\n- 问题：如何引导更有用的输出","x":-560,"y":-480,"width":460,"height":180},
		{"id":"node_12_sft","type":"text","text":"### 1.2 SFT：人类示范微调\n- 人类编写指令-答案对\n- 让模型学习偏好与风格\n- 输出更聚焦、更有用","x":-60,"y":-480,"width":460,"height":160},
		{"id":"node_source_file","type":"file","file":"Sources/CuboxSync/ChatGPT模型的三层理解 - 张浩在路上-2023-09-07.md","x":-840,"y":-840,"width":300,"height":180},
		{"id":"node_original_link","type":"link","url":"https://imzhanghao.com/2023/02/24/chatgpt/","x":-840,"y":-620,"width":300,"height":60},
		{
			"id":"label_impl",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"模型实现（关键细节）",
			"styleAttributes":{"border":"invisible","textAlign":"center"},
			"x":700,
			"y":-520,
			"width":280,
			"height":40
		},
		{"id":"node_impl_arch","type":"text","text":"### 架构要点\n- Transformer（decoder-only）\n- 位置编码/注意力机制\n- 大规模分布式训练","x":440,"y":-480,"width":460,"height":160},
		{"id":"node_impl_sft","type":"text","text":"### SFT 细节\n- 高质量指令-响应集\n- 交叉熵微调\n- 提示模板化","x":440,"y":-300,"width":460,"height":150},
		{"id":"node_impl_rlhf","type":"text","text":"### 强化学习细节\n- PPO + KL 惩罚\n- 探索与稳定性的权衡\n- 采样-评价-更新流水线","x":440,"y":-120,"width":460,"height":160},
		{"id":"node_final_safety","type":"text","text":"### 4.1 安全\n- 微软 Tay、FB 标签事故\n- 语言模型灵活但风险更高\n- 护栏与红队至关重要","x":-560,"y":200,"width":460,"height":160},
		{"id":"node_14_rlhf","type":"text","text":"### 1.4 RLHF（PPO）\n- 策略：语言模型\n- 奖励：RM − KL(约束偏离SFT)\n- 循环：采样→打分→更新\n- 目标：更对齐、更稳健","x":-60,"y":-260,"width":460,"height":180},
		{"id":"node_13_rm","type":"text","text":"### 1.3 奖励模型（RM）\n- 人类对多个候选排序\n- 学习偏好评分函数\n- 高分>低分，捕捉质量差异","x":-560,"y":-260,"width":460,"height":160},
		{
			"id":"label_last",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"写在最后",
			"styleAttributes":{"border":"invisible","textAlign":"center"},
			"x":-300,
