			"width":280,
			"height":40
		},
		{"id":"node_final_cost","type":"text","text":"### 4.2 成本\n- 数据：GPT‑3 级别TB量级\n- 算力：数千 PF‑days\n- 训练/推理成本巨大，单位交互有成本","x":-60,"y":200,"width":800,"height":200},
		{"id":"node_train_image","type":"link","url":"https://oss.imzhanghao.com/img/202302240527749.png","x":40,"y":300,"width":400,"height":220},
		{"id":"node_hist_gpt1","type":"text","text":"### GPT‑1（2018）\n- 无监督预训练 + 监督微调\n- 提出预训练迁移范式","x":1440,"y":-480,"width":460,"height":140},
		{"id":"node_hist_gpt3","type":"text","text":"### GPT‑3（2020）\n- 175B 参数\n- few‑shot / In‑context","x":1440,"y":-300,"width":460,"height":140},
		{"id":"node_hist_instructgpt","type":"text","text":"### InstructGPT（2022）\n- 指令学习 + 人类反馈\n- 对齐至人类偏好","x":1440,"y":-120,"width":460,"height":140},
