		{"id":"node_hist_instruction","type":"text","text":"### Instruction Tuning（FLAN等）\n- 多任务指令微调\n- zero‑shot 提升显著","x":1940,"y":-300,"width":460,"height":140},
		{"id":"node_hist_chatgpt","type":"text","text":"### ChatGPT\n- 训练方式与InstructGPT一致\n- 数据采集与交互形态差异","x":1940,"y":-120,"width":460,"height":140},
		{"id":"node_link_ziegler","type":"link","url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/1909.08593","x":1440,"y":60,"width":460,"height":501},
