		{"id":"node_impl_data","type":"text","text":"### 数据与分词\n- Web/书籍/代码混合数据\n- BPE/Tokenizer\n- 清洗去噪与去重","x":940,"y":-480,"width":460,"height":160},
		{"id":"node_impl_rm","type":"text","text":"### RM 细节\n- Pairwise 排序/BT模型\n- 负对数似然目标\n- 质量信号更稳定","x":940,"y":-300,"width":460,"height":150},
		{"id":"node_impl_safety","type":"text","text":"### 安全与对齐\n- 毒性/偏见过滤\n- 拒答/护栏策略\n- 系统提示与政策","x":940,"y":-120,"width":460,"height":160}
